  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 400&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked, then once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
